list of provided tools
----------------------

simpledigen
===========
simple dictionary generator - make passwords of a given
length, consisting of lowercase letters.


ppmp
===========
Password Pipe Mangling Program is a tool to generate
common variations out of the passwords provided on stdin.
it can do things like add number on the begin/end, reverse
passwords, make anagrams, lower case, upper case, etc...
in general it provides a set of passwords for each entry on
given input.
